deprecation.message:
Please note, a newer package is available Microsoft.Identity.Client. 
This package will continue to receive critical bug fixes until December 2022, we strongly encourage you to upgrade.
See https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/active-directory/develop/msal-net-migration for Migration guide and more details.

description: This package contains the binaries of the Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL). ADAL provides easy to use authentication functionality for your .NET client and Windows Store apps by taking advantage of Windows Server Active Directory and Windows Azure Active Directory.
